enum ItemInfoEnums::InfoTypeFilter
 

Enum for filtering the ItemInfo in the search match.

Enumeration values:
All  All item info. No filtering at all.
OneSearch_All  All item info:s for onesearch request.
None  No item info shall be returned.

const char* ItemInfoEnums::infoTypeToString (  LangTypes::language_t  lang,
ItemInfoEnums::InfoType  t,
const char *  defVal = NULL,
bool  smsish = false
)  [static]
 

Uses StringTable to get a string representing the type of key sent in.

If the language is not found, another language (english) will be used. If no string is found, defVal will will be returned.

Parameters:
lang The requested language.
t The requested info type.
defVal Default value to return if not found.
